    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>前言：</h3>

<p>最近按照XDite寫的Rails101實踐在MAC建置Ruby on Rails環境，期間遇到不少問題，現將其問題解法或偷吃步寫下，給自己一個教訓</p>

<h4>安裝失敗的環境設置</h4>

<ul>
<li>OS版本：Lion 10.7.2</li>
<li>Xcode版本：4.2.1</li>
<li>RVM版本：1.10.1</li>
</ul>


<h4>問題說明</h4>

<p>安裝總會出現錯誤
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>ERROR: Error running './installer -a
</span><span class='line'>/Users/APPLE/.rvm/rubies/ree-1.8.7-2011.03 --no-tcmalloc
</span><span class='line'>--dont-install-useful-gems ', please read
</span><span class='line'>/Users/APPLE/.rvm/log/ree-1.8.7-2011.03/install.log
</span><span class='line'>ERROR: There has been an error while trying to run the ree installer. Halting
</span><span class='line'>the installation.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h4>嘗試解決過程</h4>

<p>爬文<a href="http://miau715.blogspot.com/2011/12/lionree-ruby-enterprise-edition.html">連結1</a>,<a href="http://ruby-china.org/topics/834">連結2</a>後得知xcode 4.2之後的版本已經沒有內建<a href="https://github.com/kennethreitz/osx-gcc-installer">GCC編譯器</a>，因此下載GCC並安裝完畢後，再輸入
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ rvm remove ree
</span><span class='line'>$ export CC=/usr/bin/gcc-4.2
</span><span class='line'>$ rvm install --force ree</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
結果還是出現同樣的error</p>
